<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>About the Pokémon Project</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <!-- Bulma CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.4/css/bulma.min.css">
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar is-fixed-top has-background-info">
      <div class="navbar-menu">
        <div class="navbar-start">
          <a class="navbar-item has-text-white" href="/about">About</a>
          <a class="navbar-item has-text-white" href="/pokemon">Pokémon</a>
          <a class="navbar-item has-text-white" href="/moves">Moves</a>
          <a class="navbar-item has-text-white" href="/items">Items</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- About Page Content -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="title">About the Pokémon Project</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Welcome to a project dedicated to showcasing Pokémon, their types, moves, and items. This project is designed to help users explore and learn more about Pokémon and their capabilities!</p>

        <div class="content">
          <h3 class="title is-4">Navigation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a class="has-text-info" href="/pokemon">Pokémon</a> - Explore information about your favorite Pokémon!</li>
            <li><a class="has-text-info" href="/moves">Moves</a> - Explore the various moves that Pokémon can learn.</li>
            <li><a class="has-text-info" href="/items">Items</a> - Learn about items in the Pokémon world.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      <div class="content">
          <h3 class="title is-4">What this Project Does</h3>
          <p>This website helps you find Pokémon, their moves, and items. Each Pokémon comes with details on its types, stats, and available moves. You can also explore a variety of items that may aid in battle or other activities.</p>
          <p>Though this project is still a work in progress, it is for exploring the world of Pokémon in a simple way. Future updates will include more features such as search enhancements, additional data, and interactive elements, and move pools!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>